-- Gran Colombia Gold Planning Bogota Share Listing, Republica Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-06-07T13:18:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/gran-colombia-gold-planning-bogota-share-listing-republica-says.html
Canada-based  Gran Colombia Gold Corp. (GCM) 
is preparing to list shares on Colombia’s stock exchange next
year, La Republica said, citing an interview with company
president Maria Consuelo Araujo.  The company didn’t immediately return a phone call and e-
mail requesting comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Brasilia at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
